column5: Went 5/6 over a couple days last week fishing solo at the cottage had a few other taps and follows - it was some sweet fishing  Couldnt find the 40"er i was after - but the biggest fish i have landed

Nice fish -- sometimes it can be hard to find a 40" in the Kawarthas.  BTW, you should hold them by the gill plate and not the actual gills. If you try it without the glove, you will learn right from wrong in a hurry!
